posts.title: Morning election day thread
posts.content:
This is it, our day. Today's the day we save the country. I've got no inspiring words, no reason to tell you to vote for Trump. We've done that, we know why we're voting for Trump and we're all 10000 percent in.

Today might be a day of uncomfortable conversations. Every social media you've got, every contact on your phone every person you walk by on the street.... Just utter 6 words "have you voted for Trump yet?" Some may be pissed liberals, some may be upset by this. You'll also get some hell yeah and you bet. Neither of these do we care about today.

We want the ones who may not vote. Drag them to vote. We're going to save America and they're going to help.

Bonus points. Getting liberals not to vote counts the same. Swinging a liberal to go for Trump counts for double. Getting the hell yeah I voted to do the same thing you're doing counts as 50.

Let me know how many votes you got today.

Let's save America today
